data.description: Seller will offer $5,000 in closing cost with an acceptable offer. This sprawling 5.5-acre property offers a fresh start in a serene setting. Enjoy the back deck, pool, and outdoor movie nights under the stars in complete privacy; horses are welcome too. An oversized garage easily fits ATVs, campers, and boats. Inside, find modern finishes, newer floors, and granite countertops. The first-floor primary suite is a highlight, alongside a secondary primary suite and two more bedrooms, each with its ensuite bathroom (4 beds, 4.5 baths). Peaceful country living meets convenience, minutes from Windsor, Suffolk, eateries, shops, schools, and hospitals, with an easy, no-toll commute to Norfolk. Make this your refuge today!
